    "The BLEU score for the weighted RAG model was 42.5, compared to 36.8 for the baseline model, indicating improved fluency and relevance of the generated text.",
    "Human evaluations further confirmed these findings, with the weighted RAG model receiving an average rating of 4.3 out of 5 for factual correctness and contextual relevance, compared to 3.7 for the baseline model.",
